Text:
My comment about my slow upload was a strong hint for downloaders to seed once they have finished! 

However, there doesn't seem to be much interest in this torrent - I probably didn't name it very well :(
I'm currently the only seeder on the 'Net and have only downloaded 76%.  If anyone has the complete file and is willing to seed it for a few hours, I'll seed it for the rest of the week.
ps.  You're right.  The content isn't obvious by the filename, but searching The Pirate Bay for "Drawn Together uncensored" finds it nicely!
